window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magnus and Kaitlyn have new commitments, adventures, and dangers, taking them from 1929 New York City to 1887 Montana, 1904 Paris, and to a war for their kingdom in the 24th century.<br> <br> Magnus has challenges that await. Kaitlyn has loved ones to protect. In the middle of the turmoil, they have promises they must keep.<br> <br> It all begins with a simple request: Magnus, please come....<br> <br> This is book 17 of the Kaitlyn and the Highlander series, a contemporary romance with a dash of history and a bit of sci-fi. The series must begin with book one.</p> <p>If you love mysterious heroes with desperate hearts and romantic thoughts, heroines with courage who are also very ordinary disasters, and love stories that encompass all time, then youâ€™ll love this suspenseful series.</p>"; 
